    "subject": "My Day",
    "body": "<lj-cut text=\"Sunday 7th August\">\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0022.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nGot up - and looked at the sunnyness outside\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/DSCF0024.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nGot a bus\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0026.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nStepped foot in Starbucks for the first time - too damn expensive.\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0028.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nGot coffee\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0027.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nSaw cops in Clements\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0031.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nSaw a Humvee\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0032.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nWalked a little\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0033.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nWalked a little more... and spotted cool billboard with nice backdrop\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0034.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nGot a bus to here\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0036.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nFound a church. The sky was so bluee\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0038.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nSaw baby cousin at Granny's \n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0040.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nDrove home (well, not me)\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0044.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nWent out to dinner\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0049.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nHad dinner\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0052.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nMocha Latté\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0056.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nCalled friend in America\n\n<img src=\"http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b154/-obsolete-/2005-08-07/Dscf0064.jpg\" alt=\"Bus\"/ border = \"5\">\nWatched Born on the 4th July",
